	* src/ded.c, src/dlog.c, src/dedsize.c, src/ded.h: unused-argument

	* src/ftree.c, src/ded.h, src/ded.c, src/dedsize.c, src/dlog.c, src/sortset.c, src/inline.c, src/dedwait.c, src/dedtype.c, src/dedmsgs.c:
