	* test/Makefile: renamed traceback.sh to walkback.sh

	* src/ded2s.c:
	use casts on stat-struct members to ensure that we are portable

	* src/dedsigs.c: eliminated redundant include of <signal.h>

	* src/ded.c: use new autoconf definitions of DEFAULT_EDITOR, etc.
	also, eliminated redundant includes of <signal.h> and <errno.h>

	* src/ded.h: for inclusion of <signal.h>

