1992-08-28  dickey@software.org

	* src/dlog.c: make 'read_char()' have a single return-point
	corrected 'read_script()', which was not allowing the last
	few lines of a script to be used (because the file-pointer
	was tested before testing if 'cmd_ptr' was to the end of
	'cmd_bfr')

