	consistently an interpreted string; allows me to split this
	string into scripted and non-scripted portions (to log
	the latter).

	* src/dlog.c: oops: forgot that 'rawgets_log()' returns the interpreted
	byte stream, which messed up my update for 'cmd_ptr'.
	also (same cause) must redo logic which offsets the
	logging of 'rawgets_log()'

